<article class="row">
        <div class="eleven columns">
          <h1>Welcome </h1>
          <p> <p>The Alzheimer Society London and Middlesex has been actively supporting families and individuals affected by Alzheimer's disease and other dementias since 1982. We advocate for and provide support services, education and funding for research for those affected by Alzheimer's disease and other dementias.</p>
</p>
        </div>
        <div class="four columns display">
          <figure> <img src="http://www.alzheimerlondon.ca/files/download/8250c634af57f02 " alt="" title="" width="144" height="142" /> </figure>
         </div>
      </article>
 </div>
<div class="row">
      <div class="contentDesc">

<article class="four columns block">
          <figure class="display"><img src="http://www.alzheimerlondon.ca/files/download/a664e8b25a3df1b" alt="Website Logo" title="" width="214" height="122" /> </figure>
          <a href="http://www.alzheimerlondon.ca/we-can-help" > <div class="frontcolumntitle"> We Can Help </div></a>
          <p><p>Counselling, support, and education for people with Alzheimer's disease and other dementias and their families.</p>
 </p>
     
</article>
<article class="four columns block">
          <figure class="display"><img src="http://www.alzheimerlondon.ca/files/download/1e27b42658199ec" alt="Website Logo" title="" width="214" height="122" /></figure>
          <a href="http://alzheimerlondon.ca/about-dementia" > <div class="frontcolumntitle">Living with Dementia </div></a>
          <p><p>A diagnosis of dementia affects families and friends as well as the person with the disease. Learn how to help, support and reassure those living with dementia.</p>
</p>
      
</article>
<article class="four columns block none">
          <figure class="display"><img src="http://www.alzheimerlondon.ca/files/download/90402818c0f3df2" alt="Website Logo" title="" width="214" height="122" /></figure>
         <a href="http://alzheimerlondon.ca/we-can-help/program-and-services/resource-centre" > <div class="frontcolumntitle">Resources</div></a>
          <p><p>Reference works, videos, and information on Alzheimer's disease and other dementias. Visit the online catalogue.</p>
</p>
   
</article>


